ENTRY       EC 4.2.3.81                 Enzyme
NAME        exo-alpha-bergamotene synthase;
            trans-alpha-bergamotene synthase;
            LaBERS (gene name)
CLASS       Lyases;
            Carbon-oxygen lyases;
            Acting on phosphates
SYSNAME     (2E,6E)-farnesyl diphosphate lyase (cyclizing, (-)-exo-alpha-bergamotene-forming)
REACTION    (2E,6E)-farnesyl diphosphate = (-)-exo-alpha-bergamotene + diphosphate
SUBSTRATE   (2E,6E)-farnesyl diphosphate [CPD:C00448]
PRODUCT     (-)-exo-alpha-bergamotene;
            diphosphate [CPD:C00013]
COMMENT     The enzyme synthesizes a mixture of sesquiterpenoids from (2E,6E)-farnesyl diphosphate. As well as (-)-exo-alpha-bergamotene (74%) there were (E)-nerolidol (10%), (Z)-alpha-bisabolene (6%), (E)-beta-farnesene (5%) and beta-sesquiphellandrene (1%).
